Given a time in AM/PM format, convert it to  24 hour time.

Input: 
05:40:30PM

Expected Output
17:40:30

Hint: Consider edge cases for eg 12 am in the morning and 12 midnight should get converted appropriately.

Why? - Helps you learn to convert Strings to integers and do basic string manipulation. Also serves as a good introduction to  
conditionals.  

Expected time to solve: 10 mins to  1 hour

Source: HackerRank
